aboutpara: I'm Jay Henderson, a co-owner of Still Life photography. We are a group of creative photographers and content creators. Capturing the perfect moment is our skill. Enhancing and preserving it is our specialty. To us even the tiniest details are important, for they determine how a captured moment will be remembered. Still Life photography invites you to come see the world though our lense and allow us to help preserve your special moment in time.
